ingredientsDesc:
1. I-125 Anti-FSH Reagent (Red): 3 (or 6) vials, 5.4 ml per vial, containing fluorescein and iodine-125 labelled      mouse monoclonal antibodies to FSH, <370 kBq per vial, in phosphate buffer containing normal sheep serum, bovine serum albumin (BSA), inert dye and sodium azide 0.2%, w/v.

2. FSH MAIAclone Calibrator 0 mIU/ml: 3.0 ml per vial, containing bovine serum with sodium azide, 0.2% w/v.

    FSH MAIAclone Calibrators 0.5- 2- 10- 25- 75 and 150 mIU/ml: 1.0 ml per vial, precalibrated at 0.5- 2- 10-    25- 75 and 150 mIU/ml of FSH per ml (2nd IRP 78/549) in bovine serum with sodium azide, 0.2% w/v.

3. FSH MAIAclone Separation Reagent: 1 vial (33.0 ml), containing sheep antiserum to fluorescein covalently bound to magnetic particles in Tris buffer with BSA and sodium azide, 0.1% w/v.
